{"tid":806749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人對中央信任度跌","createTime":"2018-09-05T03:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T17:28:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbac05a2260e4526fa340b7ee660c1c20a8bd8a","tid":806749,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180905/20492284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180905%2F20492284&d=475R2aNBn2CFmojb1lVusdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=d02919c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180905%2F20492284&h=1ea36c97\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180905/20492284</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月05日 <br />\n<br />\n港人對中央信任度跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180905/large/05la5p41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F05la5p41.jpg&h=40aa9fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大民調顯示，港人對中央政府的信任度下跌，不信任度略增。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【中大民調】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國家主席習近平連任接近半年，香港人對中央政府的信任度下跌、不信任度略為增加，反而香港人對港府的信任度變得中間化，信任度與不信任度均有所減少。至於行政長官林鄭月娥方面，市民對她的評分則輕微下降。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭評分微降<br />\n<br />\n中大亞太研究所上月底就中港兩地的政府信任度、林鄭月娥民望等問題成功訪問了710位市民。民調結果顯示港人對中央政府的信任度，由7月的24.4%減至22.5%，同時不信任度由36.3%增至36.7%，採取中間立場的「普通或一半半」亦由34.3%上升至35.1%。<br />\n<br />\n香港政府方面，香港人的最新信任度是31.8%，較7月減少1.4個百分點，不信任度亦由7月的21.4%減至最新的20.1%，反而信任度為「普通或一半半」則有2.1個百分點的增長。連帶港人對港府的滿意度及不滿度同樣下跌，兩者的最新比率分別是28.2%及31.3%。<br />\n<br />\n至於港人對林鄭月娥的評分，雖由7月的56.7分減至最新56.2分，但與一年前她上場首個月相比，則有2分進賬。按受訪者年齡及學歷劃分的話，年紀越輕、學歷越高的人繼續是不滿林鄭的主因，30歲以下人士對她的評分更低至48.9分。<br />\n<br />\n反而按社會階層劃分的話，受訪者表示自己為下層或中下層的人士，對林鄭月娥評分最低，中上層或上層人士則給予林鄭較高分數。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n議員發起聯署抗689律師信攻勢"},{"pid":"ebd13adca6d4808a0ab41ae77877879ad7e16284","tid":806749,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:47:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">徙鳩氣啦，一日香港仲有班愛支病仲有支那DNA，一日都唔會有負數！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e79613acbf5abbecd868bce6cc49fbb17ad0c6a4","tid":806749,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/114838_f502b6b6152b8129066b2bbc5833df01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F114838_f502b6b6152b8129066b2bbc5833df01.gif&h=7728de46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c3d0d67fcf169d0ac73a31785d8bb7202a6f85e","tid":806749,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"到底要幾蠢先會信共狗"},{"pid":"f107d0c6858bd6f88b7bd2f3113b2ab50e92a2a8","tid":806749,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c3d0d67fcf169d0ac73a31785d8bb7202a6f85e","tid":806749,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"到底要幾蠢先會信共狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:24:14.000Z","msg":"有著數個班好撐架"},{"pid":"f157d80b33c56d700a78d3360cee31802d834c18","tid":806749,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"自認中國人會撐"}]}